  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h2 id=\"Integrations:WebhooksandAPIs-EnhanceYourIntegrationCapabilitieswithWebhooksandAPIIntegration\">Enhance Your Integration Capabilities with Webhooks and API Integration</h2><p>RepairQ offers webhooks and API features designed to streamline your operations and enhance integration capabilities. Users on our Professional plan can take advantage of webhooks available in reporting. For details on API integration, please <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.servicecentral.com/contact/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>contact us</strong></a> for specifications and licensing information.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Control - f79824.png\" width=\"776\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2471034883/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Integrations:WebhooksandAPIs-WhatareWebhooks?\">What are Webhooks?</h2><p>Webhooks are a way for different applications to communicate with each other in real-time. They allow one system to send data to another when specific events occur, such as adding a new customer. This automation can save time and ensure your customer lists are always up-to-date.</p><h3 id=\"Integrations:WebhooksandAPIs-WebhooksinRepairQ\">Webhooks in RepairQ</h3><p>Using webhooks with RepairQ helps streamline your operations, save time, and improve the accuracy of your marketing efforts by automatically sending your Customer List to Mailchimp. Reporting Automation is available to users on our Professional Plan.</p><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1937014890\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automating Customer Lists to Mailchimp through Zapier</a></p></li></ul><h2 id=\"Integrations:WebhooksandAPIs-WhatareAPIs?\">What are APIs?</h2><p>APIs (Application Programming Interfaces) are sets of rules and protocols that allow different software applications to communicate with each other. APIs enable your business software to seamlessly connect with other applications, such as CRM systems, accounting software, and marketing platforms like Mailchimp. This integration ensures data consistency and streamlines operations across different tools.</p><h3 id=\"Integrations:WebhooksandAPIs-APIsinRepairQ\">APIs in RepairQ</h3><p>By using APIs, you can automate routine tasks, such as updating customer information, creating appointments, processing tickets, and managing inventory. This reduces manual effort and increases efficiency.</p><ul><li><p>To utilize these features, please <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.servicecentral.com/contact/\" rel=\"nofollow\">contact us</a> for specifications and licensing information.</p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936982118\" rel=\"nofollow\">RepairQ API - Embed Qsite\u2122 Ticket Status Into Your Website</a></p></li></ul><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
